# Python Modules - Curso em Vídeo

This repository contains custom Python modules and packages created during the "Curso em Vídeo" Python course (World 3).

##  Skills & Topics Covered
* Modular Architecture and Package Creation (`__init__.py`)
* Separation of Concerns (Business Logic vs. UI)
* String Formatting and Terminal Tables
* Robust Data Validation and Error Handling (`try/except`)

##  Project Structure
* `/useful/numbers`: Math and currency operations.
* `/useful/string`: Terminal UI and text formatting.
* `/useful/data`: Safe user input validation.
